{"tid":1420335,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[!集思!] 光復香港 時代革命","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T19:25:47.000Z","uid":50238,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ec43317549737203fbe2b25f1b30c50041e411d9","tid":1420335,"uid":50238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:17:59.000Z","msg":"見好多人都講緊應唔應該keep依句口號。不如大家講下你對依句既諗法<br />\n<br />\n我覺得香港已經沈淪, 係因為被一班不是真心以香港利益為出發點既政府官員及親中派議員控制。<br />\n所以要光復香港, 令政府還政於民！<br />\n<br />\n革命係指社會政權或制度上得到「由下而上」嘅反對行動而有所改變，香港市民對現今政府不信任，所以需要普選去作出依個改變！<br />\n<br />\n我覺得只要攪清大家既諗法，喺而家唔好觸碰其他太具爭議／唔多人支持既想法，可以繼續叫依個口號。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求　缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港　時代革命！"},{"pid":"00ec5938fca435cc2ab8b9ac63820fd1eb34fac2","tid":1420335,"uid":50238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"1d7dbd4751d4c09926281e747cc6fa0961010db4","tid":1420335,"uid":50238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:18:23.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"a7b16b7ab251944bb273ca5e13cdc5dc4b647a5d","tid":1420335,"uid":50238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:18:35.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"1adcdc5e3b0e1645971a59894bb384dcdcf023d0","tid":1420335,"uid":50238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:18:45.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"7e6847593d4941de977f303880ce1e957586e194","tid":1420335,"uid":50238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:18:56.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"d75a932670f37e2a06b4b205a1918071deabbf7d","tid":1420335,"uid":50238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:19:06.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"d3bd6825dcbcd730392bf922de8af5e5a5382bb8","tid":1420335,"uid":50238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:19:16.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"6f27047f353f189cad22631d5e2fa46e162df586","tid":1420335,"uid":50238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T0